i-MSCP Mailman plugin ChangeLog
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.2
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Fixed: Entity with status set to 'disabled' must not be counted by the getItemWithErrorStatus() plugin method
	Fixed: The IP address used in the Apache vhost must match the IP address of the domain
	Fixed: The IPv6 addresses in the Apache vhosts must be enclosed in square brackets
	Fixed: Wrong DNS resources record added when an IPv6 address is used

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.0.1
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	Release: First released version
